classDiagram
    class Module
    Module : +forward()
    Module : +parameters()
    
    class LinearRegressionModel {
        +nn.Linear linear_layer
        +__init__(input_dim, output_dim)
        +forward(x)
    }
    
    Module <|-- LinearRegressionModel : Inherits
    
    class TrainingLoop {
        +Optimizer adam
        +LossFunction mse
        +train(epochs)
    }
    
    LinearRegressionModel --> TrainingLoop : Model passed to Optimizer
    
    note for LinearRegressionModel "The forward pass defines how input x becomes prediction y_hat"
